<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, September 28 (Xinhua) -- The general price index on
Tehran Stock Exchange on Monday stood at 1,531.75, up 0.57 points
from Sunday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 1,178,264 shares changed hands in 844 turns and the
turnover was 3.782 billion rials (about 687,000 U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
Shares of 45 manufacturing units made gains while those of 13
others decreased. 
</P>
</TEXT>
