<HEADLINE> Evening Performance Marks Flood-Fighting Victory </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 28 (Xinhua) -- A large televised
evening performance was held today in the studios of China Central
Television (CCTV) to mark the victory of this year's
flood-fighting campaign.
</P>
<P>
Representatives of the flood-fighting heros and the
people and the army from the 8 flood-hit provinces and
autonomous regions watched the performance, which featured praise
for the flood-fighting achievements and the people's glorious
spirit during the campaign.
</P>
<P>
Many art forms, including music, singing, dance and short
drama, were represented on the stage, as television stations in
the eight flood-hit provinces and autonomous regions joined CCTV
in sponsoring the event.
</P>
<P>
Ding Guangen, a member of the Political Bureau of the Central
Committee of the Communist Party of China (CPC) and head of the
Department of Publicity of the CPC Central Committee, attended the
performance.  
</P>
