in a larger and more fruitful co-operation with your great
country," said the Romanian Prime Minister, expressing his hope
that Romanians would enjoy Schroeder's visit to Bucharest as soon
as possible, "which would be a positive sign of bilateral
relations being relaunched."
</P>
<P>
