<HEADLINE> China Holds National Day Reception for Overseas Chinese (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Referring to the Asian financial turmoil, Qian expressed
sympathy for the losses suffered by local Chinese, and said the
Chinese government is deeply concerned about attacks on
Chinese-Indonesians in Indonesia.
</P>
<P>
He also praised Tung Chee Hwa for his effective performance in
fighting against the Asian financial crisis.
</P>
<P>
As Hong Kong is now in an economic readjustment period, the
Hong Kong people are sure to go through temporary difficulty, he
noted.
</P>
