the motherland. With the example of Hong Kong's smooth return, the
participation of the Macao compatriots, and cooperation between
China and Portugal, Macao will surely realize a smooth return and
transfer of power, he said.
</P>
<P>
Addressing the Taiwan issue, Qian said cross-straits political
dialogue has been put on the agenda, and he hopes the Taiwan
authorities will comply with the trend of the times and do
something practical for peaceful reunification.
</P>
