Addressing the gathering, Guangzhou mayor Lin Shusen said that
despite the negative influence of the Asian financial crisis and a
weak domestic market, Guangzhou from January to August achieved a
10.7 percent growth in its gross domestic product compared with
the same period last year.
</P>
<P>
He expressed sincere gratitude on behalf of the city
government to all domestic and foreign friends that care about
Guangzhou's economic development and social progress. 
