<HEADLINE> Macao Unemployment Rate Hits 5.1 Percent </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MACAO, September 29 (Xinhua) -- The unemployment rate in Macao
hit 5.1 percent between June and August this year, the latest
official statistics show.
</P>
<P>
According to figures released by the Macao Census and
Statistics Department on Tuesday, the jobless rate rose by 0.4
percent from the May-July period this year.
</P>
<P>
During the June-August period last year, the jobless rate stood
at 3.2 percent.
</P>
<P>
The underemployment rate went down 0.1 percent to 1.3 percent
from the May-July period this year.
</P>
<P>
Macao has seen an economic slowdown since 1993. 
</P>
