<HEADLINE> Leftist Party Leaders Face Arrest in Turkey </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, September 28 (Xinhua) -- The chief prosecutor at the
Ankara State Security Court demanded Monday that Chairman of the
leftist Workers' Party (IP) Dogu Perincek and eight of his
colleagues be arrested.
</P>
<P>
The semi-official Anatolia News Agency reported that the
prosecutor, whose name was not disclosed, accused Perincek and his
