<HEADLINE> Flash: Albanian Prime Minister Resigns </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Tirana, September 28 (Xinhua) -- Albanian Prime Minister Fatos
Nano resigned on Monday, his ruling Socialist Party Spokesman Musa
Ulqini said. 
</P>
